@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:18080
@sessionKey = demo-session-{{$timestamp}}
@username = hb_{{$timestamp}}
@password = 123456
@token =
@providerId = coding-plan

### 0) 首页
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Accept: application/json

### 1) 健康检查
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

### 2) 注册（首次跑）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

> {%
  if (response.body && response.body.data && response.body.data.token) {
    client.global.set("token", response.body.data.token);
    client.log("token set from register");
  }
%}

### 3) 登录（重复跑推荐用这个）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

> {%
  if (response.body && response.body.data && response.body.data.token) {
    client.global.set("token", response.body.data.token);
    client.log("token set from login");
  }
%}

### 4) 当前登录态
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 5) 聊天（同步）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionKey": "{{sessionKey}}",
  "userId": "{{username}}",
  "message": "你好，介绍一下你能做什么",
  "channel": "api"
}

### 5.1) 聊天（JVM 参数，验证自动工具获取）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionKey": "{{sessionKey}}",
  "userId": "{{username}}",
  "message": "帮我获取当前进程的JVM启动参数，直接给参数列表",
  "channel": "api"
}

### 6) 聊天（触发项目检索技能）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionKey": "{{sessionKey}}",
  "userId": "{{username}}",
  "message": "我不知道路径，帮我找 ChatServiceImpl 在哪个文件，并给我核心方法名",
  "channel": "api"
}

### 6.1) 聊天（触发工作区任务分析，更像 Agent 找实现）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionKey": "{{sessionKey}}",
  "userId": "{{username}}",
  "message": "帮我分析 ChatServiceImpl 的核心实现在哪，顺便给我关键代码片段",
  "channel": "api"
}

### 6.2) 聊天（验证“项目中是否存在某文件/配置”不会再退回要路径）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionKey": "{{sessionKey}}",
  "userId": "{{username}}",
  "message": "项目中是否存在 Spring AI 相关文件，请直接告诉我有哪些",
  "channel": "api"
}

### 7) 聊天（触发天气技能）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionKey": "{{sessionKey}}",
  "userId": "{{username}}",
  "message": "帮我查一下北京今天天气",
  "channel": "api"
}

### 8) 聊天（触发汇率技能）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionKey": "{{sessionKey}}",
  "userId": "{{username}}",
  "message": "帮我查 1 美元等于多少人民币",
  "channel": "api"
}

### 9) 聊天（触发新闻技能）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionKey": "{{sessionKey}}",
  "userId": "{{username}}",
  "message": "帮我查今天 AI 相关新闻，给我 3 条",
  "channel": "api"
}

### 10) 聊天（列出可用脚本技能）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionKey": "{{sessionKey}}",
  "userId": "{{username}}",
  "message": "有哪些 skill 可以直接帮我做事？",
  "channel": "api"
}

### 10.1) 查询脚本 skill 目录（热发现）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/manage/script-skills
Accept: application/json

### 10.1.1) 查询模型提供方与当前活动模型
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/manage/model-providers
Accept: application/json

### 10.1.2) 切换活动模型提供方（例如 coding-plan / qwen / primary）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/manage/model-providers/switch
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "providerId": "{{providerId}}"
}

### 10.1.3) 切换指定 provider 内的具体 model（例如 coding-plan -> qwen3-coder-plus）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/manage/model-providers/switch
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "providerId": "coding-plan",
  "model": "qwen3-coder-plus"
}

### 10.2) 重载脚本 skill 目录（新增/修改 skill 后调用）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/manage/script-skills/reload
Accept: application/json

### 10.3) 聊天（脚本技能：项目分析）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionKey": "{{sessionKey}}",
  "userId": "{{username}}",
  "message": "请用 repo_inspector 帮我分析 Spring AI 相关文件",
  "channel": "api"
}

### 10.4) 聊天（脚本技能：运行诊断）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionKey": "{{sessionKey}}",
  "userId": "{{username}}",
  "message": "请用 runtime_probe 看看 18080 端口被谁占用了",
  "channel": "api"
}

### 10.5) 聊天（脚本技能：天气兜底）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionKey": "{{sessionKey}}",
  "userId": "{{username}}",
  "message": "如果天气工具失败，就改用 weather_fallback 查北京天气",
  "channel": "api"
}

### 11) 聊天（流式）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/stream
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "sessionKey": "{{sessionKey}}",
  "userId": "{{username}}",
  "message": "请总结你刚才查到的信息",
  "channel": "api"
}

### 12) 记忆检索（按会话）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/memory/search?sessionKey={{sessionKey}}&query=天气&topK=6
Accept: application/json

### 13) 审计日志分页
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/audit/logs?page=1&size=20&userId={{username}}
Accept: application/json

### 14) 审计统计
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/audit/stats?recentLimit=500
Accept: application/json

### 15) 后台总览
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/manage/overview
Accept: application/json

### 16) 查询用户（需 db-enabled=true）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/manage/users
Accept: application/json

### 17) 写入工具权限（需 db-enabled=true）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/manage/tool-permissions/upsert
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roleCode": "USER",
  "toolName": "WebSearchToolPack.webSearch",
  "allow": true,
  "priority": 10,
  "enabled": true
}

### 18) 重载 SOUL
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/soul/reload
Accept: application/json

### 19) 模拟飞书 Webhook（本地）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/webhook/feishu
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event": {
    "sender": {
      "sender_id": {
        "open_id": "ou_test_user_001"
      },
      "sender_type": "user"
    },
    "message": {
      "chat_id": "oc_test_chat_001",
      "message_id": "om_test_msg_{{$timestamp}}",
      "message_type": "text",
      "content": "{\"text\":\"你好，来自飞书 webhook\"}"
    }
  }
}
